# Repo-wide Docker build context exclusions.
# Applies to every `docker build .` run from the repo root.

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin
**/obj
**/*.user
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
coveragereport/
dotnet-coverage/
**/TestResults/

# Node / Angular artifacts
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.angular
**/coverage
**/.sass-cache
**/tmp

# IDE
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/

# Secrets
**/secrets.json
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/.env

# VCS / docs
.git/
.github/
.claude/
docs/screenshots/
*.md
!data/documents/*.md

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
